videos.description: Devon Dotson grabs the rebound and leads the fast break, finding Lagerald Vick for a 3-pointer to extend the Jayhawks' early lead.
videos.headline: Dotson feeds Vick for transition triple

videos.description: Quentin Grimes drives to the hoop and gets around De'Quon Lake, finessing one off the glass for a smooth finish.
videos.headline: Grimes spins layup off glass for crafty finish

videos.description: L.uguentz Dort crosses up Quentin Grimes, then soars to the rim for the huge two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Dort takes off for two-handed slam

videos.description: Dedric Lawson pushes in transition and spins away from Zylan Cheatham to finish with the finger roll.
videos.headline: Lawson schools defender with spin and score

videos.description: Luguentz Dort can't finish on the inside, but Romello White stays with the play and finishes through contact for the tough 3-point play.
videos.headline: White powers up for and-1 putback

videos.description: Zylan Cheatham loses the ball, but Luguentz Dort recovers it and finds him on the inside for the thunderous dunk.
videos.headline: Cheatham rocks rim with two-handed jam

videos.description: Luguentz Dort glasses David McCormack's layup, then Taeshon Cherry flips home the fast-break finish on the other end.
videos.headline: Dort stuffs, Cherry scores

videos.description: Devon Dotson gives it off to Lagerald Vick, who nails a triple despite the contact from Luguentz Dort for a clutch 4-point play.
videos.headline: Vick quiets crowd with 4-point play

videos.description: Remy Martin comes off the screen and connects on a pull-up jumper to give the Sun Devils a 78-76 lead with under a minute left.
videos.headline: Martin drains go-ahead bucket late in 2nd half

videos.description: Devon Dotson can't handle Lagerald Vick's pass, causing a crucial turnover in the final seconds of the game against Arizona State.
videos.headline: Kansas throws ball away in final seconds

videos.description: After trailing through the first 34 minutes, the Sun Devils hit some clutch shots and stifle the Jayhawks down the stretch for an 80-76 upset win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Arizona State rallies to knock off No. 1 Kansas) 2018/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Arizona State rallies to knock off No. 1 Kansas
